title: How It Works Book of Amazing Technology - 2013
description:
How It Works Book of Amazing Technology - 2013

212 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 59 MB 


Your complete guide to understanding how gadgets, gizmos and everyday devices work. From the people behind the best-selling How it Works magazine. Featuring: Entertainment - Amazing internal views of all the best games consoles and entertainment systems. Domestic - A look at your household day-to-day technology. Gadgets - From 3D cameras to iPhones and tablets, we dissect these top devices. Inventions - Examining how these amazing pieces of kit came to be.
